item.title: SECon Robotics Announcements
item.description: Please remember to post on the wiki about the pros/cons of the concepts we have been discussing as we need to progress forward in design. There are also no more New Member meetings, so any questions you or anyone you know may have, please come to the meeting on Tuesdays at 6pm in Broun 235 and ask us.

item.title: SECon Robotics Announcements
item.description: SPaRC Meetings have been moved from Mondays @ 4pm to Tuesdays from 6-7pm. This is a permanent change with all meeting occuring on Tuesdays now. Email me (sparcwebmaster@gmail.com) about questions or confilcts. Also, New Member meetings will begin on Tuesday, August 26th at 5pm in Broun 239.
